{"tid":1389061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全部人推聲援,葵芳出真槍同打記者,天水圍煙花post, 天水圍的PR對與錯就由佢沉","createTime":"2019-07-30T21:08:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T10:53:27.000Z","uid":8301,"like":58,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b7ea7b4d816963ff5a96680e4d8b69167669b595","tid":1389061,"uid":8301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:08:53.000Z","msg":"頭先講得唔清楚比巴打屌所以開過<br />\n<br />\n唔逐個post入去講了, 你覺得TSW係PR野既更加應該推正經post(聽日聲援, 葵槍真槍指市民,天水圍煙花) 唔好比對手PR宣傳, 你開POST講到點勁都好最後都一定係唔會有答案加只係會屌到自己人,我相信無人會因為有一兩個正常警察就會對警黑合作既印象改觀, 但係我地都無必要幫對手宣傳, 所以請大家集中火力推以下post (借用巴打template)<br />\n<br />\n731凌晨事件整合<br />\n1:黑警用實彈槍指示威人士 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1388402/page/5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1388402/page/5</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1388908/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1388908/page/1</a><br />\n其中<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10157350582524929&amp;set=a.396735049928&amp;type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10157350582524929%26set%3Da.396735049928%26type%3D3%26theater&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=7f9cc6f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10157350582524929&amp;set=a.396735049928&amp;type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n2:天水圍有白衣人士向途人施放煙火<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/y3nn9?fbclid=IwAR3z6ew7Q5H_QayrEG1BCF-TTshbrM1Or6QJl6DihZPmuSrTMJAVN2YH7qE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fy3nn9%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3z6ew7Q5H_QayrEG1BCF-TTshbrM1Or6QJl6DihZPmuSrTMJAVN2YH7qE&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=4dc299fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/y3nn9?fbclid=IwAR3z6ew7Q5H_QayrEG1BCF-TTshbrM1Or6QJl6DihZPmuSrTMJAVN2YH7qE</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://sendvid.com/1j0fhidn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsendvid.com%2F1j0fhidn&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij7P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=636fe532\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://sendvid.com/1j0fhidn</a><br />\n<br />\n3:天水圍有警員向市民舉中指<br />\n<br />\n4:［有片！］葵芳站警車突然加速衝向人群！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1388748/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1388748/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n5:[有片]岩岩葵湧有防暴追住記者狂打 仲要係用盾打頭 用棍追打 當記者係狗咁趕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1388549\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1388549</a>"},{"pid":"6e53a0664d66f768bc2b5c85043b5ce829a37a27","tid":1389061,"uid":8301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:12:52.000Z","msg":"真係有人講9203就用以下template"},{"pid":"11270ef2d599d4b739fef81b0a3ac66e3f86602a","tid":1389061,"uid":8301,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:13:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【分析】天水圍放煙花係一場傑出PR</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由千夫所指到主持大局</span></strong><br />\n抗議者包圍警署，原本警察只能被動地被圍屌。但當外面馬路突然放煙花，然後即刻有個外表上鏡、似足TVB警察劇主角既藍衫出黎講野，呼籲救人要緊。<br />\n放煙花之後，抗議者由抗議警察執法不公，變成市民尋求警察保護。放煙花之後，現場由抗議警權，係「救人要緊」既大旗下，急速逆轉成由警察「主持大局」，甚至因此得到掌聲。「執法不公」、拘捕學生時「濫用暴力」、「警黑合作」完全被放埋一邊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時間天衣無縫</span></strong><br />\n放煙花時間，剛好安排在3位學生被釋放之後數分鐘；「驅散人群」的觀感大減，始終釋放學生就，追究執法不公的關注度就會降低。然後一放煙花，「救人要緊」就自然完全蓋過追究執法不公。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一洗落閘「唔做野」形象</span></strong><br />\n天水圍警署比人屌得最勁，就係7.21落閘唔做野。但今次一反常態地，幾個警察即刻衝出黎「執法」。趁抗議者同記者齊哂人，係鏡頭面前高調「做野」，一洗「唔做野」既形象。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">帶領輿論，追究警黑合作</span></strong><br />\n假車牌、玩煙花、南亞人；事件明顯係有組織既行動。究竟乜野人策劃？放煙花對乜野人最有利？只要扣連係警黑合作既脈絡下思考，答案根本好明顯。但我地需要既，係將依件事分析比大眾知道，唔可以比「民意翻盤」依件事發生。"},{"pid":"8e65b171aafcd16a4567afe43132071c24cd3d01","tid":1389061,"uid":279604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:15:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5e4760b9b0f1a3f0413df425de866fc1c5b96a7b","tid":1389061,"uid":279604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:15:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"bb2e8fe347d6c97d7260e632d82c9937bab8c819","tid":1389061,"uid":37504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:15:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「有片有證據」30/7 無勇武義士扮記者攻擊任何人，不要被分化</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1388962\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1388962</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫推澄清"},{"pid":"8789f739107841693283d460a268c6631af7de7b","tid":1389061,"uid":279604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:15:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4b04076bd8da26939a49df669254bd3fdf0db141","tid":1389061,"uid":63321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:17:01.000Z","msg":"Why not both?"},{"pid":"3300a48d87a580893b3e399d05c8ac6b35071808","tid":1389061,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:17:12.000Z","msg":"天水圍係恐襲<br />\n警黑合作"},{"pid":"9586c80175859796d8b34dc7c9fe6f34a9633384","tid":1389061,"uid":279604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:17:12.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5cb82f55f884bc6d67db9852d28e410bb35bdb01","tid":1389061,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:19:56.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n光頭佬渣槍已經夠晒料做文宣<br />\n煙火單嘢手頭上嘅資料未足夠，等各位起底"},{"pid":"5ced05b00e2cfd14cb0f16d95c7f13affe894734","tid":1389061,"uid":8301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:24:32.000Z","msg":"總之PR之戰就由佢唔好推啦, 有人認為可以反過黎對黑警用good cops bad cops戰術, 有人覺得一定唔得, 但係最終結論一定係屌自己人(上立場篇文睇下就知支持同反對應該係一半半左右), 每當有二元對立就一定有世戰大戰上晒熱門, 結果就益晒政黑警"},{"pid":"189a596ba6892c632294a102609d867df2431a35","tid":1389061,"uid":8301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T21:29:58.000Z","msg":"731凌晨事件整合<br />\n1:黑警用實彈槍指示威人士 <a href=\"https://l